<%- include('../partials/header', { title: 'I\'m a Teapot - Ella Rises', user: typeof user !== 'undefined' ? user : null }) %>

<!-- 418 Teapot page - fun error page -->
<style>
    /* Teapot container styles */
    .teapot-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 70vh;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5 0%, #e8e8e8 100%);
    }

    /* Floating teapot animation */
    .teapot-animation {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        position: relative;
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* Float animation keyframes */
    @keyframes float {
        0%, 100% {
            transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(5deg);
        }
    }

    .teapot-body {
        width: 120px;
        height: 100px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 100%);
        border-radius: 50% 50% 50% 50% / 60% 60% 40% 40%;
        position: relative;
        margin: 0 auto;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .teapot-spout {
        width: 40px;
        height: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513 0%, #A0522D 100%);
        border-radius: 0 50% 50% 0;
        position: absolute;
        right: -30px;
        top: 30px;
        transform: rotate(-10deg);
    }

    .teapot-handle {
        width: 30px;
        height: 60px;
        border: 8px solid #8B4513;
        border-left: none;
        border-radius: 0 50px 50px 0;
        position: absolute;
        left: -20px;
        top: 20px;
    }

    .teapot-lid {
        width: 100px;
        height: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A0522D 0%, #8B4513 100%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        top: -10px;
        left: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .teapot-knob {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        background: #654321;
        border-radius: 50%;
        position: absolute;
        top: -25px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .steam {
        position: absolute;
        top: -40px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 4px;
        height: 40px;
        background: rgba(200, 200, 200, 0.6);
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: steam-rise 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .steam:nth-child(2) {
        left: 45%;
        animation-delay: 0.3s;
        height: 50px;
    }

    .steam:nth-child(3) {
        left: 55%;
        animation-delay: 0.6s;
        height: 45px;
    }

    @keyframes steam-rise {
        0% {
            opacity: 0.6;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0) scale(1);
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0.3;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px) scale(1.2);
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-40px) scale(1.5);
        }
    }

    .teapot-number {
        font-size: 8rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        color: #8B4513;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .teapot-message {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #333;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    .teapot-subtitle {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #666;
        margin: 0.5rem 0 2rem 0;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .teapot-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        background: #8B4513;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3);
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .teapot-button:hover {
        background: #A0522D;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.4);
    }

    .teapot-facts {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        max-width: 600px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .teapot-facts h3 {
        color: #8B4513;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    }

    .teapot-facts p {
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
</style>

<div class="teapot-container">
    <div class="teapot-animation">
        <div class="steam"></div>
        <div class="steam"></div>
        <div class="steam"></div>
        <div class="teapot-body">
            <div class="teapot-lid">
                <div class="teapot-knob"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="teapot-spout"></div>
            <div class="teapot-handle"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="teapot-number">418</div>
    <div class="teapot-message">I'm a teapot</div>
    <div class="teapot-subtitle">The server refuses to brew coffee because it is, permanently, a teapot.</div>
    
    <a href="/" class="teapot-button">Return Home</a>
    
    <div class="teapot-facts">
        <h3>â˜• Fun Fact</h3>
        <p>The HTTP 418 status code was created as an April Fools' joke in 1998. It's a real status code that means "I'm a teapot" - a reference to the Hyper Text Coffee Pot Control Protocol (HTCPCP). While it's not commonly used in production, it's a fun way to handle requests that can't be fulfilled!</p>
    </div>
</div>

